thread.title: Chad Dix
thread.title_full: National Storage reviewed by Chad Dix

author: Chad Dix
title: Chad Dix
text: A hassle free experience from beginning to end! The live chat made the initial inquiry very easy to find a perfect storage solution along with a follow up from call to confirm all the details. Adrian from the Moonah centre then phoned to ensure I had all the information I needed and to organise a viewing of the site and space. Very helpful and friendly. I would recommend National Storage to anyone who is after a convenient experience at very competitive prices.
